tels  resorts inc from january 8 to october  and executive vice president and chief financial officer of canadian pacific limited from january  to december  during the time span of august  to january  he served as vice president of finance  accounting and chief financial officer of canadian pacific limited from august 88 to august  mr fatt served as a vice president and treasurer of canadian pacific limited he also worked as the chief executive officer of legacy hotels real estate investment trust since june  mr william has been the vice chairman of legacy hotels real estate investment trust he also served as a member of the investment nominating compensation compliance and governance committees mr william has also been the director of enbridge gas distribution inc since 8 mr fatt also served as a director of doubletree corp and of its general partner doubletree partners since december 3 william r fatt obtained a bachelor of arts in economics from york university fairmont hotels and resorts is one of the canada based operators of a number of plush hotels and resorts across the globe lately it is operating buildings across 8 countries including canada  the united states  mexico  bermuda  barbados  monaco  germany  of switzerland  egypt  kenya  united kingdom  tanzania  south africa  the united arab emirates  oman  saudi arabia  china and singapore  in canada the famous and legendary hotels of fairmont are the fairmont empress in victoria bc hotel vancouver in vancouver fairmont royal york in toronto the château frontenac in quebec city or the banff springs hotel in banff alberta     categories people   hotel  resort insider  hotel  resort insider llc  privacy policy including use of cookies  terms and conditions  about  contact  help  advertise  tell a friend readers contribution mediakit fatt william r  canadian pacific insider transactions  tipranks go prologin  sign up follow✓get real time transactionsinsider detailsfatt william rcanadian pacific cpdirector not ra