 of frhi hotels  resorts he is currently a member of the board of directors of the jim pattison group inc and the bank of nova scotia previously mr fatt was chairman of the board of cadillac fairview corporation and a director of encana corporation sun life financial inc and enbridge inc mr fatt holds a ba economics from york university mr fatt brings to the board over 3 years of finance investment capital markets and international experience source canadian pacific railway limited on 3   sign up for equilar atlas and view william r fatts full profile by accessing equilar atlas you can view bios network salary and wealth events of industryleading executives like william r fatt more specifically youll be able to identify corporate executives in william r fatts network and community follow changes in william r fatts employment and moneyinmotion connect with william r fatt through your network of conections view full profile   search for over 36 executive profiles bio example william r fatt william r fatts connections 8 sign up now to view william r fatts 8 connections » stephen d mcdonald former group head global corporate and investment banking and cochief executive officer global banking and markets the bank of nova scotia sarabjit s marwah former vice chairman and chief operating officer the bank of nova scotia john h clappison former board member rogers communications inc indira v samarasekera former board member the bank of nova scotia ronald a brenneman former president and chief executive officer petrocanada j michael durland former group head and chief executive officer global banking and markets the bank of nova scotia brian j porter former president and chief executive officer the bank of nova scotia c james prieur board member manulife financial corporation ralph s cunningham former president and chief executive officer enterprise gp holdings paul d sobey dir former president and chief executive officer empire company limited popular profiles sign up now to